      <description>&lt;p&gt;slug: The-Birth-of-Our-Metaverse-English-Club&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In 2024, I co-founded a club that quickly became one of my favorite projects: the &lt;strong&gt;Metaverse English Research Club&lt;/strong&gt;. What makes this club special is its commitment to creating a fun, interactive, and immersive learning environment. We wanted to break the fear often associated with learning English, replacing it with curiosity and joy.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&#xA;  class=&#34;image-figure not-prose my-8&#34;&#xA;  data-lightbox-enabled=&#34;&#xA;    true&#xA;  &#34;&#xA;  data-gallery-type=&#34;auto&#34;&#xA;  data-image-width=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;  data-image-height=&#34;0&#34;&#xA;  data-image-src=&#34;https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*wE1tThuwR_9woGiKdj-V7A.png&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;image-container&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*wE1tThuwR_9woGiKdj-V7A.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;VR English Club&#34;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;    decoding=&#34;async&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-src=&#34;https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/1*wE1tThuwR_9woGiKdj-V7A.png&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-alt=&#34;VR English Club&#34;&#xA;    data-gallery-title=&#34;&#34;&#xA;  /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
